					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Going by the code in the pastebin links, it looks like the reset routine does not jump to MainGameLoop it instead returns to nothing at the last line. The main code mistakenly starts out with a subroutine call to reset but that never happens because the RESET vector correctly points to the reset routine.<br /><br />P.S. Welcome to the nesdev forums, this is an excellent first post.</div>

