						<div class="postbody"><tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">jsr reset</tt> is also problematic in this case as the reset routine also resets the stack pointer therefore making that <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">rts</tt> still return to nothing.</div>

